{"id": "a4c7b9ea51b74a1284bf4136c6e5d9ef83039acbaa6f94224ae4e2bfb089ebd8", "item_id": "6934757cd6:0", "text": "To add a user attribute to an object, we add it via the Edit Parameter Interface."}
{"id": "12a0c0a38a81d17260e5e61ea567f7c6022cc17bb5c25e66d63ea704f87d6cea", "item_id": "6934757cd6:1", "text": "Add a parameter to the User tab under either the Attributes or Primvars section in the RenderMan tab. The parameter must be located within the User folder and must be prefixed \"ri_user_\" to be read."}
{"id": "9efc5c389d265dfcfbaf2630f1952757381cabc967f15e6fd768f2b57fc5950a", "item_id": "6934757cd6:2", "text": "You must also supply a Tag Value to the parameter to inform Houdini and RenderMan of the type and allow interactive edits."}
{"id": "53c732bab0242ef0ce1b3889f8087c1acec296f9dc78acc8ef3f7004b384202a", "item_id": "6934757cd6:3", "text": "Setting up MatteID as an Example"}
{"id": "cce01ce55b2ab50f0814b270b8126bebe42c2e4e2f0fa3f9e06809c077af7a34", "item_id": "6934757cd6:4", "text": "Create a color attribute called \"ri_user_MatteID0\"."}
{"id": "397f9e7e3d2609643926d4bb4606edb92c787a98cb0004f9a99ab895b6bd05dc", "item_id": "6934757cd6:5", "text": "The label is the UI displayed name."}
{"id": "e661a0a824eb9491690c86a3810e8ac16f6fb03e1377c8c57b7700ac8f1ac825", "item_id": "6934757cd6:6", "text": "Note we have used the tags field near the bottom, this is to inform Houdini and RenderMan of the RenderMan attribute. Valid types of values are listed below."}
{"id": "059f5d260bf9dbb2ec2298e7c988771c2eb783a4b42a499f3676e58667494fe2", "item_id": "6934757cd6:7", "text": "Valid Tag Values are listed here. These must match the expected data type of the Parameter chosen in the left hand pane called \"Create Parameters\":"}
{"id": "6da88c34ba124c41f977db66a4fc5c1a951708d285c81bb0d47c3206f4c27ca8", "item_id": "6934757cd6:8", "text": "int"}
{"id": "76a7e234dc54e9c605b2cc9fdf71279526150df48c574bdfa69e436e0b3d5c18", "item_id": "6934757cd6:9", "text": "float"}
{"id": "251fecd592e56e6c4a95121752f4a73bb802dffc1cc4bce6100206ee2b7cb650", "item_id": "6934757cd6:11", "text": "point"}
{"id": "b0d51c58c8b9c1f458fadf16c7d375630ef51da4df81915893b05c0fa4ed8bc6", "item_id": "6934757cd6:12", "text": "vector"}
{"id": "317b32c143692b9939c197f6a5df54f9698df9a4882fe8bf19608968662be4fa", "item_id": "6934757cd6:13", "text": "normal"}
{"id": "8674aab0dfc2483b62c5b5f10c167037acb4fcd9cea122db7913c747ac7d2efb", "item_id": "6934757cd6:14", "text": "hpoint"}
{"id": "6e00cd562cc2d88e238dfb81d9439de7ec843ee9d0c9879d549cb1436786f975", "item_id": "6934757cd6:15", "text": "matrix"}
{"id": "473287f8298dba7163a897908958f7c0eae733e25d2e027992ea2edc9bed2fa8", "item_id": "6934757cd6:16", "text": "string"}
{"id": "26ded777e9b5659ed9e120efa70a225b4b397e0d582705998c7fd0011b5c5203", "item_id": "6934757cd6:17", "text": "This will emit the following to the RIB."}
